message_1: Consider the cryptographic hash function SHA-256. If you input the message "hello world" into the SHA-256 hash function, what is the resulting hash code in hexadecimal form?
message_2:
To compute the SHA-256 hash of the message "hello world", you can use a programming language or an online tool. Here's the resulting hash code in hexadecimal form:
